146
00:13:52,096 --> 00:13:53,523
That's what I want to say.

147
00:13:53,608 --> 00:13:54,903
Are you insane?

148
00:13:55,164 --> 00:13:56,326
You told me to trust you,

149
00:13:56,410 --> 00:13:57,961
and you went on and did that?

150
00:13:58,046 --> 00:13:59,720
Why did you run your car over?

151
00:13:59,805 --> 00:14:00,850
What?

152
00:14:01,673 --> 00:14:04,487
I could've run over Chae Yoori,
but I held it in. Was what I did wrong?

153
00:14:04,572 --> 00:14:06,424
You've really lost it.

154
00:14:09,899 --> 00:14:13,610
Why won't your face turn back to normal?

155
00:14:13,817 --> 00:14:15,400
I don't know.

156
00:14:15,920 --> 00:14:17,244
It just happened.

157
00:14:17,612 --> 00:14:19,108
Then, how did it turn back?

158
00:14:19,224 --> 00:14:21,013
I don't know that either.

159
00:14:21,679 --> 00:14:23,049
It just happened.

160
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:26,060
As if there was ever a valid reason.

161
00:14:27,498 --> 00:14:29,571
What an unpredictable disease.

162
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,563
Whatever.

163
00:14:32,124 --> 00:14:33,825
When I heard you're not coming back,

164
00:14:33,909 --> 00:14:36,055
