She must have had a hard time.
Look at her. She's so thin.

170
00:14:50,809 --> 00:14:52,302
What are you talking about?

171
00:14:52,387 --> 00:14:53,902
I fed her very well.

172
00:14:54,048 --> 00:14:55,217
I'm sure you only fed yourself.

173
00:14:55,302 --> 00:14:57,000
I even bought her snacks.

174
00:14:57,085 --> 00:14:58,755
