So she couldn't appear on TV these days.

177
00:15:05,271 --> 00:15:06,586
Isn't she pregnant?

178
00:15:06,699 --> 00:15:09,088
Someone I know said,
she saw her at the hospital.

179
00:15:09,173 --> 00:15:12,017
Nonsense. Her manager was
hospitalized, remember?

180
00:15:12,107 --> 00:15:13,208
She might be there to visit her.

181
00:15:13,577 --> 00:15:16,334
Be careful with your words.
These days, if you misspeak...

182
00:15:16,478 --> 00:15:17,902
... you can get sued.

183
