197
00:16:14,991 --> 00:16:15,968
I don't remember.

198
00:16:16,712 --> 00:16:18,181
Was it my stylist?

199
00:16:18,506 --> 00:16:20,010
Or was it my manager?

200
00:16:20,299 --> 00:16:21,754
Anyway, someone gave it to me.

201
00:16:22,785 --> 00:16:24,156
What could it be?

202
00:16:24,241 --> 00:16:25,636
I really have no idea.

203
00:16:25,721 --> 00:16:27,452
