204
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:29,508
Hi, Segye.

205
00:16:30,326 --> 00:16:31,989
It's Han Segye.

206
00:16:34,669 --> 00:16:35,584
What's this?

207
00:16:35,794 --> 00:16:37,330
