555
00:36:48,431 --> 00:36:50,388
What are you talking about? I am mean.

556
00:36:50,473 --> 00:36:52,417
Gosh. You all are just so adorable.

557
00:36:54,468 --> 00:36:56,720
You siblings sure have problems.

558
