You always want things the easy way.

574
00:38:14,207 --> 00:38:15,125
You caught me.

575
00:38:17,602 --> 00:38:18,967
Do you want to...

576
00:38:19,699 --> 00:38:22,367
... come in and eat some ramyun?

577
00:38:23,307 --> 00:38:25,952
You always want things the easy way.

578
00:38:26,447 --> 00:38:27,848
Do I look like an easy person to you?

579
00:38:27,933 --> 00:38:28,904
Who?

580
00:38:29,830 --> 00:38:30,690
Me?

581
00:38:52,815 --> 00:38:53,955
What are you looking at?

582
00:38:58,859 --> 00:39:00,100
You're awake...

583
00:39:00,988 --> 00:39:02,414
... but why are you leaning on my shoulder?

584
00:39:03,061 --> 00:39:04,906
You know I'm awake...

585
00:39:06,546 --> 00:39:08,152
... but why are you not doing anything?

586
00:39:10,529 --> 00:39:11,701
Why aren't you asking me?

587
00:39:13,141 --> 00:39:14,024
Whether...

588
00:39:15,061 --> 00:39:16,820
... I've decided to be a priest...

589
00:39:17,801 --> 00:39:18,789
... or not.

590
00:39:18,874 --> 00:39:21,614
If you tell me you are going to be one,
at this point...

591
00:39:22,755 --> 00:39:23,680
... then...

592
00:39:25,406 --> 00:39:27,287
... you're really a mean person.

593
00:39:28,827 --> 00:39:30,014
That's not good.

594
00:39:31,236 --> 00:39:32,653
I'm a nice guy.

595
00:39:44,487 --> 00:39:46,231
Is it because I'm too nice?

596
00:39:47,479 --> 00:39:49,184
It really drove me crazy...

597
00:39:50,026 --> 00:39:51,997
... when I thought...

598
00:39:55,057 --> 00:39:56,619
... you were going to that jerk.

599
00:40:03,051 --> 00:40:04,040
I guess...

600
00:40:06,367 --> 00:40:07,858
... I'm just too nice.

601
00:40:13,212 --> 00:40:14,149
No.

602
00:40:15,256 --> 00:40:16,467
You're really mean.

603
00:40:22,282 --> 00:40:23,878
You're extremely...

604
00:40:26,569 --> 00:40:27,791
... terrible.

605
00:40:39,309 --> 00:40:43,695
Face blindness?

606
00:40:44,408 --> 00:40:46,936
That's the easy way to explain it.

607
00:40:47,279 --> 00:40:48,827
The medical term for it...

608
00:40:49,407 --> 00:40:51,037
... is prosopagnosia.

609
00:40:51,856 --> 00:40:53,447
So...

610
00:40:53,600 --> 00:40:55,969
... you can't distinguish faces...

611
00:40:56,117 --> 00:40:57,612
I was in a car accident.

612
00:40:58,189 --> 00:40:59,504
I injured my brain...

613
00:41:00,013 --> 00:41:01,832
... and this condition
was the result of it.

614
00:41:03,958 --> 00:41:06,144
I'm not just a little confused...

615
00:41:07,118 --> 00:41:10,375
... I can't recognize
people's faces at all.

616
00:41:13,735 --> 00:41:15,273
So that's why...

617
00:41:15,543 --> 00:41:17,543
... I've caused you a lot of inconvenience.

618
00:41:17,888 --> 00:41:21,421
It'll probably going to be
a lot more troublesome in the future.

619
00:41:21,573 --> 00:41:23,302
I ask for your understanding in advance.

620
00:41:26,402 --> 00:41:27,726
I thought...

621
00:41:28,355 --> 00:41:32,071
... I should personally tell you all.

622
00:41:33,624 --> 00:41:35,536
(A place to rest in the sky)

623
00:41:36,304 --> 00:41:39,406
So that's why he noticed
every tiny detail.

624
00:41:40,029 --> 00:41:41,422
From your new hairstyle...

625
00:41:41,547 --> 00:41:42,981
... to him getting an ear-piercing.

626
00:41:43,940 --> 00:41:45,860
We're so oblivious...

627
