... and were making bets about it.

628
00:41:47,899 --> 00:41:50,603
I feel sorry for him.
He must have gone through a lot.

629
00:41:50,793 --> 00:41:55,322
Manager Lee, will it be okay if people
find out about Mr. Seo's condition?

630
00:41:55,443 --> 00:41:56,942
Of course, it won't be okay.

631
00:41:57,131 --> 00:42:00,953
I'm sure he's willing to take the risks
to get what he wants.

632
00:42:01,064 --> 00:42:02,797
Why would it not be okay?

633
00:42:03,160 --> 00:42:05,318
I better be okay.

634
00:42:05,403 --> 00:42:08,372
If something happens, I won't sit back.

635
00:42:08,577 --> 00:42:11,804
