But you've got some nerves.

766
00:48:37,170 --> 00:48:38,003
What?

767
00:48:38,464 --> 00:48:39,391
You've been nice?

768
00:48:39,575 --> 00:48:41,414
Why do you think I was easy on you?

769
00:48:42,595 --> 00:48:44,021
Because you can help me?

770
00:48:44,574 --> 00:48:45,987
Because I was scared of you?

771
00:48:46,953 --> 00:48:47,961
Not at all.

772
00:48:48,334 --> 00:48:50,348
There's only one reason.

773
00:48:50,913 --> 00:48:52,130
My sister.

774
00:48:53,628 --> 00:48:56,150
But now that my sister has dumped you...

775
00:48:56,403 --> 00:48:58,403
... I no longer have any reasons...

776
00:48:59,075 --> 00:49:00,293
... to put up with you.

777
00:49:06,996 --> 00:49:08,676
So what are you going to do now?

778
00:49:09,445 --> 00:49:12,453
Trash needs to be treated like trash.

779
00:49:15,065 --> 00:49:16,512
You...  stop...

780
00:49:17,665 --> 00:49:18,941
Don't you dare hit me.

781
00:49:19,038 --> 00:49:20,427
Hit you?

782
00:49:21,420 --> 00:49:22,299
Me?

783
00:49:23,860 --> 00:49:24,823
Hey.

784
00:49:25,513 --> 00:49:30,578
Why do you think I have a fish tank
that can fit a person in my office?

785
00:49:45,726 --> 00:49:46,661
Get lost.

786
00:49:47,243 --> 00:49:48,508
Don't come here ever again.

787
00:49:48,979 --> 00:49:50,979
