792
00:50:03,381 --> 00:50:04,372
Joohwan.

793
00:50:05,155 --> 00:50:06,541
Show him the way out.

794
00:50:12,811 --> 00:50:16,052
How could you do a fansign event
in this situation?

795
00:50:16,137 --> 00:50:17,486
I told you to cancel it.

796
00:50:18,032 --> 00:50:19,901
I have to work at times like this.

797
00:50:20,578 --> 00:50:23,324
It's even better
if I can show them my face.

798
00:50:23,750 --> 00:50:27,353
My fans need to see my face
to feel reassured.

799
00:50:28,111 --> 00:50:31,550
That's because you've trained them
well over the years.

800
00:50:33,513 --> 00:50:34,422
It's Han Segye.

801
00:50:34,507 --> 00:50:36,093
Segye, you're so pretty.

802
00:50:36,751 --> 00:50:37,683
My gosh.

803
00:50:41,053 --> 00:50:42,546
(Han Segye Fansign Event)

804
00:50:47,567 --> 00:50:48,794
You're so pretty.

805
00:50:48,879 --> 00:50:50,455
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

806
00:50:52,163 --> 00:50:53,559
I'm a big fan.

807
00:50:53,644 --> 00:50:55,802
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

808
00:50:56,185 --> 00:50:57,469
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

809
00:51:00,273 --> 00:51:01,211
Segye...

810
00:51:01,788 --> 00:51:03,035
... can you see my eyes?

811
00:51:03,119 --> 00:51:04,243
What's wrong with your eyes?

812
00:51:04,402 --> 00:51:05,358
Are you hurt?

813
00:51:06,957 --> 00:51:10,125
I don't ever do overtime at work,
but you make me work all the time.

814
00:51:11,000 --> 00:51:12,000
Look, my eyes are bloodshot.

815
00:51:13,025 --> 00:51:15,437
Segye, can you please
stop getting into trouble?

816
00:51:15,522 --> 00:51:17,522
I stay up late every night
replying to comments.

817
00:51:18,458 --> 00:51:19,497
