855
00:53:22,336 --> 00:53:24,336
While he was still married to my mom...

856
00:53:25,281 --> 00:53:26,995
... he left for Europe alone.

857
00:53:27,681 --> 00:53:29,092
He left both me and my mom behind...

858
00:53:29,989 --> 00:53:31,210
... and just left.

859
00:53:33,286 --> 00:53:35,920
But nonetheless,
he was still a father to me.

860
00:53:37,806 --> 00:53:40,511
While living our own lives
like strangers...

861
00:53:42,048 --> 00:53:44,772
I heard that my father
was in critical condition.

862
00:53:46,162 --> 00:53:47,301
Before he died...

863
00:53:48,387 --> 00:53:50,289
... he said he wanted to see me.

864
00:54:09,105 --> 00:54:10,145
I just arrived.

865
00:54:10,825 --> 00:54:12,707
I'm on my way out
after stopping by the hotel.

866
00:54:13,156 --> 00:54:14,997
I'm heading straight
to the hospital where he's at.

867
00:54:15,082 --> 00:54:16,691
I'll head over as soon as I can.

868
00:54:17,053 --> 00:54:17,898
I'm sorry.

869
00:54:17,983 --> 00:54:19,469
I'll go first and wait for you.

870
00:54:19,980 --> 00:54:21,198
Please...

871
00:54:21,833 --> 00:54:22,759
... don't be late.

872
00:55:00,958 --> 00:55:02,051
Oh my gosh.

873
00:55:02,136 --> 00:55:03,048
What happened?

874
00:55:03,132 --> 00:55:04,164
Call 911.

875
00:55:04,197 --> 00:55:05,704
Call the ambulance.

876
00:55:05,796 --> 00:55:06,922
He's badly hurt.

877
00:55:07,007 --> 00:55:08,253
Call for an ambulance.

878
00:55:10,806 --> 00:55:13,188
-Is he okay?
-There has just been an accident.

879
00:55:13,273 --> 00:55:14,095
What's the address here?

880
00:55:14,224 --> 00:55:16,262
-97, Prince Street.
