881
00:55:19,281 --> 00:55:20,398
Is she okay?

882
00:55:21,095 --> 00:55:22,344
Oh my gosh. Someone call 911.

883
00:55:22,429 --> 00:55:23,347
Ma'am?

884
00:55:23,432 --> 00:55:24,526
Ma'am, are you hurt?

885
00:55:28,719 --> 00:55:30,093
Are you hurt? Ma'am?

886
00:55:41,519 --> 00:55:42,577
What happened?

887
00:55:42,661 --> 00:55:43,563
It was a car crash.

888
00:55:43,647 --> 00:55:44,934
He lost a lot of blood.

889
00:55:45,464 --> 00:55:47,293
His blood pressure is really weak.

890
00:55:47,378 --> 00:55:49,039
We must get him to surgery right now.

891
00:55:49,124 --> 00:55:50,215
Go faster.

892
00:55:51,002 --> 00:55:52,224
Please stay with us.

893
00:55:52,309 --> 00:55:53,752
Hurry. Hurry.

894
00:55:53,861 --> 00:55:55,123
Come on.

895
00:55:55,256 --> 00:55:56,277
-Run.
-Go ahead.

896
00:55:56,362 --> 00:55:57,344
Run!

897
00:56:51,129 --> 00:56:52,279
Dojae...

898
00:57:00,888 --> 00:57:02,145
Dojae.

899
00:57:05,518 --> 00:57:06,676
Dojae...

900
00:58:40,549 --> 00:58:42,025
My son...

901
00:58:43,476 --> 00:58:45,406
You should get up soon.

902
00:58:49,346 --> 00:58:51,173
Wake up...

903
00:58:53,316 --> 00:58:55,033
... and meet your dad.

904
00:59:35,701 --> 00:59:36,743
Can you hear me?

905
00:59:36,827 --> 00:59:38,042
Give me some signal.

906
00:59:38,409 --> 00:59:39,310
Are his pupils normal?

907
00:59:39,395 --> 00:59:40,341
Yes, normal.

908
00:59:40,463 --> 00:59:42,379
What about his heartbeat? Is it stable?

909
00:59:42,844 --> 00:59:44,372
-Yes, stable.
-Dojae.

910
00:59:46,495 --> 00:59:47,578
Who...

911
00:59:49,609 --> 00:59:50,487
... are you?

912
01:00:02,734 --> 01:00:04,333
And like that, ten years passed by.

913
01:00:18,698 --> 01:00:19,533
I...

914
01:00:22,282 --> 01:00:24,034
I need to go home.

915
01:00:24,917 --> 01:00:25,948
Now?

916
01:00:32,107 --> 01:00:34,371
I have something to do.

917
01:00:37,847 --> 01:00:39,085
I'm sorry.

918
01:00:39,882 --> 01:00:41,020
I'll take you home.

919
01:00:41,105 --> 01:00:42,007
No.

920
01:00:43,321 --> 01:00:44,330
It's fine.

921
01:00:46,089 --> 01:00:47,366
Then, I'll just walk you
to the front door.

922
01:00:47,451 --> 01:00:49,279
It's okay. I can go out on my own.

923
01:00:50,155 --> 01:00:51,447
I can go alone.

924
01:00:52,119 --> 01:00:53,612
Is it something urgent?

925
01:00:55,614 --> 01:00:56,483
Yes.

926
01:00:57,050 --> 01:00:58,152
It's urgent.

927
01:01:00,222 --> 01:01:01,182
