930
01:01:11,453 --> 01:01:12,715
... of having a famous girlfriend.

931
01:01:15,153 --> 01:01:16,315
Take care on your way home.

932
01:01:16,745 --> 01:01:18,207
Call me when you get home.

933
01:01:52,392 --> 01:01:53,285
You...

934
