-Can I help you?
-Don't I look better than her?

938
01:02:08,562 --> 01:02:09,734
But can you tell the difference?

939
01:02:10,023 --> 01:02:11,905
You don't know how I feel
right now, do you?

940
01:02:12,605 --> 01:02:13,438
Right.

941
01:02:14,731 --> 01:02:16,731
You can't even remember me anyway.

942
01:02:23,100 --> 01:02:24,874
I practiced as I watched them.

943
01:02:25,458 --> 01:02:27,264
I practiced distinguishing people.

944
01:02:27,645 --> 01:02:29,116
Although it was no use.

945
01:02:29,431 --> 01:02:32,143
