I have never loved myself.

946
01:02:32,411 --> 01:02:33,624
Ever.

947
01:02:35,880 --> 01:02:37,592
How am I supposed to say it?

948
01:02:38,019 --> 01:02:40,019
When I'm a total mess?

949
01:02:40,166 --> 01:02:41,670
I'm not okay.

950
01:02:41,920 --> 01:02:42,988
It's not okay for me.

951
01:02:44,559 --> 01:02:46,176
I want to see you.

952
01:02:47,976 --> 01:02:49,478
I want to recognize you.

953
01:02:52,854 --> 01:02:54,729
What should I do?

954
01:02:57,055 --> 01:02:59,759
I feel so guilty. What should I do?

955
01:03:26,241 --> 01:03:28,513
I don't deserve to be with him.

956
01:03:28,834 --> 01:03:30,319
How dare I smile?

957
01:03:30,403 --> 01:03:32,189
How dare I be happy?

958
01:03:32,712 --> 01:03:35,300
I don't deserve it all.

959
01:04:26,731 --> 01:04:29,879
(Uncle)

960
01:04:38,697 --> 01:04:40,308
Did you get home safely?

961
01:04:43,824 --> 01:04:46,017
