962
01:04:47,710 --> 01:04:49,744
I keep regretting letting
you leave like that.

963
01:04:59,180 --> 01:05:00,354
Han Segye?

964
01:05:01,841 --> 01:05:03,186
Seo Dojae...

965
01:05:03,977 --> 01:05:05,290
... listen carefully.

966
01:05:09,999 --> 01:05:12,659
You became like that because of me.

967
01:05:14,006 --> 01:05:15,464
What do you mean?

968
01:05:16,784 --> 01:05:19,364
It's my fault that you became like that.

969
01:05:48,850 --> 01:05:51,358
(Beauty Inside)

970
01:05:51,477 --> 01:05:54,598
