972
01:05:57,944 --> 01:05:59,811
I don't know who else to call,

973
01:05:59,895 --> 01:06:01,253
that's why I called you.

974
01:06:01,338 --> 01:06:02,716
I feel less lonely now.

975
01:06:02,800 --> 01:06:05,369
So this woman can't live without me.

976
01:06:05,637 --> 01:06:09,258
We can't be happy if we are together.

977
01:06:09,342 --> 01:06:11,887
That's our destiny. An ill-fated one.

978
01:06:11,971 --> 01:06:13,469
I know you love me.

979
01:06:13,553 --> 01:06:14,476
Let's...

980
01:06:15,281 --> 01:06:16,319
